{
  "stem": "5654.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You see, we didn't have anybody doing our-- our cleanliness.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had to do it ourself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we learned.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This is how we learned discipline, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Despite the discipline, was there any sort of warmth?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You didn't have parents.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You just--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can't-- I don't think that we looked for that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we had our friends.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had our clique.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, and we stuck together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we share things together as much as we can, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and I can remember, you know, when we used to, at night time, we used to-- to go to the toilet, we had to go downstairs.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I-- I was somehow starving.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I went and raided the pantry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And of course, they caught me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They- they set a trap the following night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] They caught me with somebody else.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I was punished.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was put in the cellar.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in the cellar, it's-- you know, bats used to fly around.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in the dark, I got used to it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I found there was some carrots and apples, you know, in shelves.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we decided to eat there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER] So-- but this is the mischief we used to go-- we used to-- we used to do.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But, looking back, you know, it was-- it was good.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But at the same time, of course, we didn't have time to think about our parents.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because we were too many of us who were-- who were in the same situation, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when you went to and from the school every day, was there any nervousness that you would be found out?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had to be very careful, of course, that, you know, the German wouldn't notice us so much, that we were Jews.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
